cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about object recognition using neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also introduces a novel pyramidal pooling layer and encoding layer, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper evaluates and compares the proposed system to state-of-the-art computer vision methods, which could also fall under the neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
